data.description: Waterfront condo in the heart of Great Bridge. Main level features kitchen with breakfast bar, huge open family room with gas fireplace. Enjoy evening sunsets and morning coffee on the balcony with gorgeous views of the Intercoastal Waterway. Spacious penthouse primary bedroom with en-suite bath on the second level with private balcony. Walk in attic. Deeded boat slip #55 on deep water with electricity, 2 assigned parking spaces in front of unit. Condo fees include boat slip, water, sewer, trash, building exterior, grounds, clubhouse, pool and master insurance policy.
